                            <a class="icon"><Image src={Inst} alt="Instagramm" loading="lazy" /></a>
                            <a class="icon"><Image src={Fsbc} alt="Faceboock" loading="lazy" /></a>
                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                    <div class="flex flex-col p-20 gap-12">
                        <p class="meta muted">(Senior Web Developer)</p>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                            <h3 class="uppercase">David<br>Nguyen</h3>
                            <p class="medium muted">With a passion for technology and design, David crafts seamless websites that provide exceptional user experiences. His attention to detail ensures that every project runs smoothly and efficiently.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="about_info">
                    <figure class="relative">
                        <Image src={Person3} alt="person1" class="h-full w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
