                    </figure>
                    <div class="flex flex-col p-20 gap-12">
                        <p class="meta muted">(UI/UX Designer)</p>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                            <h3 class="uppercase">Emily<br>Carter</h3>
                            <p class="medium muted">Emily specializes in creating intuitive and engaging user interfaces. Her empathetic approach to design allows her to understand users' needs and develop solutions that enhance their experience.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="about_info">
