                        </figcaption>
                    </figure>
                    <div class="flex flex-col p-20 gap-12">
                        <p class="meta muted">(Graphic Designer)</p>
                        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
                            <h3 class="uppercase">Jessica<br>Chenin</h3>
                            <p class="medium muted">A talented graphic designer, Jessica brings ideas to life through stunning visuals. Her creativity and expertise ensure that every project reflects the client's brand identity and vision.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </article>
                <article class="about_info">
                    <figure class="relative">
                        <Image src={Person6} alt="person1" class="h-full w-full object-cover" loading="lazy" />
                        <figcaption class="invert dark:invert-0">
                            <a class="icon"><Image src={Twtr} alt="Twitter" loading="lazy" /></a>
